# Sakaki-iOS
### A social application for dog owners whose purpose is to help find positions for bags to collect dog excrement and to be updated in real-time on the status of the positions

### Features
- Secure login and registration using Firebase technology
![Firebase](data:image/png;base64,)

- Get bag stations based on iPhone location
![CurrentLocation](data:image/png;base64,)

- Convenient and easy-to-use navigation
![Navigation](data:image/png;base64,)

- Get details about the station in real time
![BinDetails](data:image/png;base64,)

- Update the station in an easy and convenient way
![Status](data:image/png;base64,)

- Upload a photo from the camera or choose from the photo gallery
![Photo](data:image/png;base64,)
